# Test the translate endpoint
# Make sure you have DEEPL_AUTH_KEY set in .env

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Translate text to Spanish
POST http://localhost:3000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello, world!",
  "target_lang": "ES"
}

### Translate with source language specified
POST http://localhost:3000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello, world!",
  "source_lang": "EN",
  "target_lang": "FR"
}

### Translate multiple texts
POST http://localhost:3000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": ["Hello", "Goodbye", "Thank you"],
  "target_lang": "DE"
}

### Missing required field (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello"
}
